#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.modf.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.modf"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.modf.modf:1 of
msgid "Return the fractional and integral parts of a tensor, element-wise."
msgstr "返回张量的分数部分和整数部分，按元素计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.modf.modf:3 of
msgid ""
"The fractional and integral parts are negative if the given number is "
"negative."
msgstr "如果给定数字为负数，则分数部分和整数部分也为负数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.modf.modf of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.modf.modf:6 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.modf.modf:8 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须与输入广播一致。如果未提供或为 `"
"None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）的长度必须等于"
"输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.modf.modf:13 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.modf.modf of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.modf.modf:18 of
msgid ""
"* **y1** (*Tensor*) -- Fractional part of `x`. * **y2** (*Tensor*) -- "
"Integral part of `x`."
msgstr ""
"* **y1** (*Tensor*) -- `x` 的分数部分。 * **y2** (*Tensor*) -- `x` 的整数"
"部分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.modf.modf:18 of
msgid "**y1** (*Tensor*) -- Fractional part of `x`."
msgstr "**y1** (*Tensor*) -- `x` 的分数部分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.modf.modf:19 of
msgid "**y2** (*Tensor*) -- Integral part of `x`."
msgstr "**y2** (*Tensor*) -- `x` 的整数部分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.modf.modf:22 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.modf.modf:23 of
msgid "For integer input the return values are floats."
msgstr "对于整数输入，返回值为浮点数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.modf.modf:27 of
msgid ":py:obj:`divmod`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.modf.modf:28 of
msgid ""
"``divmod(x, 1)`` is equivalent to ``modf`` with the return values "
"switched, except it always has a positive remainder."
msgstr "``divmod(x, 1)`` 等价于 ``modf``，但返回值顺序相反，且余数始终为正。"

